title: Busy Philipps Will Only Hurt a Little
description: Busy Philipps, true to her name, gets busy telling us all the ins and outs of her childhood knee injuries and life at the creek (Dawson's). We talk life, celebrity name drops, and love through the eyes of America's favorite Instagrammer. Tees are Here!!
